  "slug": "spiky-spikes",
  "title": "Spiky Spikes",
  "description": "Don't step on it! Hurts almost as much as stepping on LEGO... ouch",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Edo5jnW.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"240\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Available%20for%20Minecraft-1.19-ecebe6?labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge\" width=\"248\" height=\"28\" />&emsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Install%20on-Client%20%26%20Server-ecebe6?labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge\" width=\"240\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/spiky-spikes/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A7498\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3yrSsw7\" width=\"320\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/puzzles-lib\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3jr9xQw\" width=\"215\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/spiky-spikes/files/all?filter-status=1&amp;filter-game-version=2020709689%3A7499\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3nRXr4m\" width=\"325\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/30lZmFY\" width=\"208\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/puzzles-lib\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3jr9xQw\" width=\"215\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/forge-config-api-port-fabric\"><img src=\"https://bit.ly/3clkhvn\" width=\"299\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📖 About:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Spiky Spikes</strong> adds some really spikey spikes. There are a bunch of tiers, all with unique abilities. So what are you waiting for? Let's go and improve your mob farms!</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📚 Contents:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Spiky Spikes brings you <strong>6 Tiers</strong> of spikes, all of them are unique.</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Wooden:</strong> Slowly damages mobs, but does not deal a killing blow.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Stone:</strong> Damages and kills mobs, but does not drop any loot or experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Iron:</strong> Damages and kills mobs, only drops normal loot without experience.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Golden:</strong> Damages and kills mobs, only drops experience without any loot.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Diamond:</strong> Deals a lot of damage, mobs drop all loot like when killed by a player. Can use most sword enchantments, apply via an anvil.</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Netherite:</strong> Deals a lot of damage, mobs drop all loot like when killed by a player. Can use most sword enchantments, apply via an anvil. Is resistant to explosions and cannot be destroyed by the wither boss. Deals no damage to players.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Note:</strong> Make sure when adding enchantments to diamond and netherite spikes to have all the spikes you want to enchant ready at once. You can apply enchanted books <strong>To The Whole Stack</strong>, so enchanting more spikes later will needlessly consume more of your precious books.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>📷 Media:</strong></span></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/491/957/2022-08-31_23.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/491/958/2022-08-31_23.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Spiky spikes are spikey</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><strong>Wooden spikes bring mobs down to half a heart</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/491/959/2022-08-31_23.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/491/960/2022-08-31_23.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"231\" /></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Even the wither boss isn't safe from netherite spikes</strong></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><strong>All the enchantments you can put on spikes</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>💡 FAQ:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How do I configure this mod on Forge?</strong><br /><strong>A:</strong> Install my <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/config-menus-forge\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Config Menus for Forge</strong></span></a> mod and do it directly in-game!</span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>Q: How do I configure this mod on Fabric?</strong><br /><strong>A:</strong> Editing configs directly in-game has not yet been implemented. Instead when in a world run the <code>/config showfile &lt;modid&gt;</code> command by choosing either <code>CLIENT</code> or <code>SERVER</code> (depending on the mod), then click the file name (ending with .toml) that appears in chat to be able to manually edit the config file in a separate editor. After saving the file, the config will automatically reload in-game after a couple of seconds, so no game restart required.</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>🏆 Credits:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Developing Spiky Spikes was helped and inspired by:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/rwtema\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>RWTema</strong></span></a> for inspiring this mod from the spike blocks found in old versions of their <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/extra-utilities\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Extra Utilities</span></a> mod</span></li>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/xfacthd\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong>XFactHD</strong></span></a> for introducing me to the dark arts of rendering non-cube shapes in Minecraft</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/lunapixelstudios/projects\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=CurseForge&amp;message=LunaPixelStudios&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"282\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LunaPixelStudio\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/twitter/follow/LunaPixelStudio?label=Twitter&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"149\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://discord.gg/8ZmhaPPbjE\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/790272037578473512?label=Discord&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"220\" height=\"28\" /></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1MOyd2u.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"300\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/fuzs_/projects\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs_&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"97\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Fuzss\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzss&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"97\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2l26SuCmCNSCPefpfbCX7Q\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"89\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=@Fusseel&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=twitter&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"124\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/user/Fusseel\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=u/Fusseel&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=reddit&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Reddit\" width=\"130\" height=\"28\" /></a>&emsp;<img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Fuzs%200212&amp;color=ecebe6&amp;labelColor=2F4858&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" width=\"127\" height=\"28\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>\n<table style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/diagonal-fences\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mU9OlhP.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/air-hop\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MinxlVJ.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/stylish-effects\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/fmWwWkZ.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/enchanting-infuser-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ALHMDQn.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/easy-magic\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Mlxi8cy.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/horse-expert\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/e4TeVgY.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/tiny-skeletons-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/GCYM7Zl.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/universal-bone-meal-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q3CooZb.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/easy-shulker-boxes-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/vz0tBff.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n<td>&emsp;&emsp;</td>\n<td><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/trading-post\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UzgNFIB.png\" width=\"410\" height=\"115\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0ej6YE7.png\" width=\"854\" height=\"14\" /></p>",
